<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/meta') %>
    <title>About Us | River Stone Wyoming</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .about-container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        .about-hero { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px; }
        .about-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); }
        .mission-section { background: var(--card-bg); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 24px; padding: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .mission-section h2 { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .mission-section p { color: var(--gray-light); line-height: 1.8; }
        .stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        .stat-card { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .stat-number { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .team-section { margin-top: 60px; }
        .team-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; margin-top: 30px; }
        .team-card { background: var(--card-bg); border: 1px solid var(--glass-border); border-radius: 20px; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .team-avatar { width: 100px; height: 100px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent)); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 20px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 2.5rem; color: white; }
        .team-card h3 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .team-role { color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-hero">
            <h1>About RiverStoneWyoming <span class="gradient-text">Business</span></h1>
            <p style="color: var(--gray-light); font-size:1.2rem; max-width:700px; margin:20px auto;">Building the future of Web3 business formation—secure, compliant, and built for the modern entrepreneur.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mission-section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>We bridge the gap between traditional business formation and the rapidly evolving world of cryptocurrency and Web3. Our team combines decades of legal, compliance, and blockchain expertise to give you a single platform where you can form your LLC, verify your identity, and manage digital assets—all under one roof.</p>
            <p style="margin-top:15px;">As part of the Zen Business legacy, we bring enterprise‑grade filing accuracy and a deep understanding of what crypto founders need: speed, security, and a clear path to compliance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">5,000+</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Crypto LLCs Formed</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">50</div>
                <div class="stat-label">States Covered</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">24h</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Fastest Processing</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
                <div class="stat-label">Accuracy Guarantee</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="team-section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Leadership Team</h2>
                <p>Experts in crypto compliance and business formation</p>
            </div>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-avatar"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i></div>
                    <h3>Michael Zen</h3>
                    <p class="team-role">CEO & Founder</p>
                    <p>Third-generation business formation expert with 15+ years in the industry.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-avatar"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i></div>
                    <h3>Sarah Chen</h3>
                    <p class="team-role">Chief Compliance Officer</p>
                    <p>Former SEC counsel specializing in digital asset regulation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-avatar"><i class="fas fa-user-circle"></i></div>
                    <h3>David Park</h3>
                    <p class="team-role">Head of Crypto Operations</p>
                    <p>Blockchain architect with extensive DeFi and wallet infrastructure experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
